<h1>Welcome to Ardington House</h1>
<p class="goldBold">Ardington House has always been full of interesting people from all parts of the world and is renowned for its warm welcome and traditional hospitality.</p>
<p>I am delighted on behalf of my family to be able to offer this unique facility to all our clients who feel that the house and its beautiful grounds, gardens and lakes are suitable for their own requirements.</p>
<p>We are dedicated to ensuring that the needs of every one of our guests are carefully looked after. </p>
<p><img src="/images/index/signiture.gif" alt="Nigel Baring signiture" title="Nigel Baring signiture" /><br />
<strong>Nigel Baring</strong> - 1st Jan 2011</p>
